europeana:record.dc:description: Checklist and identification key to the pseudoscorpions of the Netherlands (Arachnida: Pseudoscorpiones) In this paper all new localities are mentioned of 23 known species of pseudoscorpions in the Netherlands. Chthonius orthodactylus (Leach, 1817), Chthonius dacnodes Nav√°s, 1918, Neobisium carpenteri (Kew, 1910) and Chernes cimicoides (Fabricius, 1793) are presented as new to the Dutch fauna. A key to identify the Dutch species is presented.
